{"tid":2433424,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tsla長線大好友沽出180萬股 稱「賣掉每一股都非常痛苦」","createTime":"2021-03-05T01:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T02:14:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60401ada95f91e8e1dd7d8bc1e7647db559ec1cb","tid":2433424,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕作為特斯拉的長期大股東的美國億萬富翁投資者拜倫（Ron Baron）週四（4日）表示，旗下投資公司Baron Capital自去年8月以來已賣出180萬股特斯拉股票，但他仍看好特斯拉股價未來10年能增至2000美元，並稱「賣掉每1股都令他非常痛苦」<br />\n<br />\n拜倫表示，他從未賣出個人持有的110萬多股特斯拉股票，並稱：「賣掉每1股都令我非常通苦。」但這次選擇這麼做是為了緩解客戶風險。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，截至2月28日，Baron Capital持有特斯拉超過610萬股股票，平均購買成本為每股42.34美元 。<br />\n<br />\nBaron Capital在去年8月到今年2月間共賣出180萬股特斯拉股票，拜倫向《CNBC》表示，有170萬股是在過去6個月裡賣出的，其中近120萬是以每股400至900美元的價格售出。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3456855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456855&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=32bcb2af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456855&h=db11f11f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3456855</a>"},{"pid":"218c45602df5f28f489a3d207a8ccc437bc21700","tid":2433424,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"但有人狂掃緊貨wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e7cb925cf424435c927618c335fbb1ab4a40fd","tid":2433424,"uid":50719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"平均購買成本為每股42.34美元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c980c08768be03cfd863c0db13312763948942f0","tid":2433424,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"笑死 明知贏都去輸"},{"pid":"e377d96bdc40e36b84fc3e5124b182c1d64baeaa","tid":2433424,"uid":35717,"like":1,"d